  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <p xml:id="Aink294-kilavi">vatuvai cellāniṉṟuḻit talaimakaṟkut tōḻi kūṟiyatu.</p>
        <p xml:lang="en"> 
          What the confidante told the hero when the marriage was going on.                 
        </p>
      </div>
      <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink294">
<l>erimaruḷ vēṅkai yirunta tōkai</l>
<l>yiḻaiyaṇi maṭantaiyiṟ ṟōṉṟu nāṭa</l>
<l>viṉitucey taṉaiyā ṉuntai vāḻiyar</l>
<l>naṉmaṉai vatuvai yayaravivaḷ</l>
<l>piṉṉiruṅ kūntaṉ malaraṇin tōyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
        <l>O man from the land where</l>
        <l>a peacock, perched on the kino-tree with flame-like [flowers],</l>
        <l>appears like a girl adorned in jewels—</l>
        <l>since what you have done is pleasing, long live your father!</l>
        <l rend="space">As the good house engages in marriage,</l>
        <l>you adorned her braided dark tresses with blossoms.</l>
        
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
